wednesday to resume talks on the occupied territories and other 
issues 
we want to keep up our meetings even if is against the emotion 
in the street right now husseini told an assembly of 100 
israelis 
the going will be tough yitzhak galnoor a peace now 
activist but once all the dust settles we see that three years 
of an uprising cannot be ignored we still have the same problem to 
solve 
during the 34monthold palestinian uprising against israeli 
occupation of the west bank and gaza strip at least 996 
palestinians have been killed and 52 israelis and foreigners have 
died 
