security council is largely symbolic as it cannot be effectively 
enforced the united nations does not allow the shooting down of 
civilian passenger aircraft 
in one brazen example of defying the sanctions an argentinian 
presidential adviser on saturday acknowledged sending 154 tons of 
beef to iraq over the past two weeks 
president carlos menem fired the adviser alberto samid for the 
embarrassing admission made more acute because argentina has 
pledged two warships to the multinational force standing up to 
saddam in the gulf region 
