recent releases rated x 
miramax sued the mpaa over its x rating for tie me up tie me 
down the company lost but a new york supreme court judge warned 
that the rating system bordered on censorship 
this just goes to show that being tenacious without waving the 
flag can get the job done said harvey weinstein miramax 
cochairman 
