four months ago 70 professors staged a sitin 
at kuwait university to protest a decree limiting the powers of 
parliament it was an act of defiance hardly imaginable in most of 
the persian gulf ruled by a collection of dictators hereditary 
monarchs and fundamentalist leaders 
