spencer of the us navy and ernest simpson a usborn british 
citizen who was a stockbroker in london 
edward abdicated because his insistence on marrying a divorcee 
created a constitutional crisis the monarch is temporal head of 
the state church of england which opposes divorce 
the duke was governor of bahamas during world war ii and 
subsequently lived in france where he died at age 77 in 1972 the 
duchess of windsor died in 1986 at age 89 
