tip some close races she said 
the operation replaces a fundraising program started 11 years 
ago in which 1000 donors were invited to washington for briefings 
on issues and social events with republican lawmakers and 
officials burnley said the inner circle is run separately from 
the nrsc which is reimbursed for staff costs she said 
the operation expects to raise as much as 115 million this 
