thursdays seasonopening performance at orchestra hall begins a 
year of programs featuring some of the orchestras greatest 
triumphs 
included will be paul duakas the sorcerers apprentice 
which chicago introduced to this country in 1899 it was 
incorporated 40 years later into the soundtrack of the disney film 
