properties 
canary wharf expected to cost 4 billion pounds 75 billion 
is olympia and yorks biggest project ever it is europes largest 
office development and boasts britains tallest building 
outside real estate agents are divided about whether the project 
will prove successful they agreed that it is a risky one because 
of its huge size and its untried hardtoreach location 
