fell 52 percent from a year earlier with 3306 deals valued at 
1512 billion announced down from 3734 deals worth 333 billion 
securities data said 
securities data said global merger activity also declined but 
the value of british transactions increased 75 percent in the third 
quarter from the second quarter 
